{"title":"docker安装gitlab","date":"2021-01-25T10:24:22.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 25, 2021","L":"01/25/2021","MM-DD":"01-25"},"link":"2021/01/25/docker-install-gitlab","tags":["gitlab"],"categories":["gitlab"],"updated":"2021-04-02T05:23:48.740Z","content":"<h2 id=\"安装运行\">安装运行<a title=\"#安装运行\" href=\"#安装运行\"></a></h2>\n<p>搜索gitlab</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker search gitlab</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>拉取gitlab镜像，其中gitlab-ce为社区版，gitlab-ee为企业版，这里我们拉取社区版即可</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull gitlab/gitlab-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>运行gitlab-ce容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -d --name gitlab \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -p 443:443 -p 80:80 -p 222:22 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    --restart always \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -v /etc/gitlab:/etc/gitlab \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -v /var/<span class=\"built_in\">log</span>/gitlab:/var/<span class=\"built_in\">log</span>/gitlab \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -v /var/opt/gitlab:/var/opt/gitlab \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    gitlab/gitlab-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><code>-v /etc/gitlab:/etc/gitlab</code> 配置文件目录映射</li>\n<li><code>-v /var/log/gitlab:/var/log/gitlab</code> 日志文件目录映射到</li>\n<li><code>-v /var/opt/gitlab:/var/opt/gitlab</code> 数据文件目录映射</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em><strong>nginx等服务的默认端口都为80，如果安装了nginx，记得修改80的端口映射</strong></em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"配置\">配置<a title=\"#配置\" href=\"#配置\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"项目地址\">项目地址<a title=\"#项目地址\" href=\"#项目地址\"></a></h3>\n<p>默认情况下，当我们创建了一个项目后，在clone的时候显示的IP地址为容器ID，这个是容器内部地址，我们在外部是无法访问的。需要将容器ID改成宿主机IP才能通过外部访问。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>查找gitlab.rb文件</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>容器中查找</p>\n<p>如果容器没有做<code>配置文件</code>目录映射，可以进入容器修改</p>\n <figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> -it gitlab /bin/bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>容器内的<code>gitlab.rb</code>文件路径为<code>/etc/gitlab/gitlab.rb</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>宿主机查找</p>\n<p>如果做了<code>配置文件</code>目录映射，可以直接在宿主机中找到该文件修改即可</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>修改gitlab.rb文件</li>\n</ul>\n<p>将<code>external_url</code>参数设置为外部主机IP即可。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 这段为原始需要修改的代码，找到该行代码修改</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># external_url 'GENERATED_EXTERNAL_URL'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 修改后的代码，假设我的宿主机IP为`192.168.222.136`</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">external_url <span class=\"string\">'http://192.168.222.136'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>重启gitlab</li>\n</ul>\n<p>修改gitlab.rb文件后，需要重启gitlab才会生效</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker restart gitlab</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"相关链接\">相关链接<a title=\"#相关链接\" href=\"#相关链接\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/poloyy/p/13968683.html\" title=\"Docker - 解决 gitlab 容器上的项目进行 clone 时，IP 地址显示一串数字而不是正常 IP 地址的问题\" target=\"_blank\">Docker - 解决 gitlab 容器上的项目进行 clone 时，IP 地址显示一串数字而不是正常 IP 地址的问题</a></li>\n</ul>\n","next":{"title":"docker安装jenkins","link":"2021/01/21/docker-install-jenkins"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2021/01/25/docker-install-gitlab/","toc":[{"id":"安装运行","title":"安装运行","index":"1"},{"id":"配置","title":"配置","index":"2","children":[{"id":"项目地址","title":"项目地址","index":"2.1"}]},{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","index":"3"}],"reward":true}